{"tid":124884,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"廣島4日3夜行程求狠批","createTime":"2017-02-18T04:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T17:35:35.000Z","uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"783191ddc25ce4749ef3863ea17129822e632bae","tid":124884,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"小弟2月中會去廣島<br />\n搭UO的<br />\n四日都同一間酒店，近本通<br />\n<br />\n第一日<br />\n下午5點到廣島，直接去本通果面放低野<br />\n行本通食野就算<br />\n<br />\n第二日<br />\n上午軍訓式起身出發大久野島<br />\n下午希望去到廣島城/博物館之類景點<br />\n<br />\n第三日<br />\n全日宮島<br />\n<br />\n第四日<br />\n上午補返第二日下午去唔到既景點<br />\n下午準備出發機場<br />\n搭下午6:00機返香港<br />\n<br />\n我之前去過一次大阪<br />\n用周遊卡搭車的<br />\n想問廣島有冇類似周遊卡的？<br />\n因為去兔島，我就咁睇都成3000円<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我怕買錯周遊卡(上網睇果啲講到唔清唔楚)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求狠批"},{"pid":"1908164f83368005b7b729e877be9e4b27c218df","tid":124884,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jry86dn5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjry86dn5&h=0728b832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去宮島一定要食呢間牡丹屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都係其他巴打推介比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個set好似有11隻蠔，分幾種煮法"},{"pid":"09254bf659207d065eb374cda7ca743013b9f442","tid":124884,"uid":64677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"宮島個日可以朝早去完原爆DOME同廣島城先去,宮島唔行上山好難玩到全日<br />\n本通近巴士中心,可以坐巴士去竹園或者尾道呢d地方"},{"pid":"05e09b44920a4528b251f167cfc769e2823fdbed","tid":124884,"uid":64677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宮島個日可以朝早去完原爆DOME同廣島城先去,宮島唔行上山好難玩到全日<br />\n本通近巴士中心,可以坐巴士去竹原或者尾道呢d地方</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8f466861c08e85c8611a04fbf5f284a3f9bb5b93","tid":124884,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"我月頭都去左4日3夜<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住：<br />\nday1 HKG  &gt; HIJ  &gt; 竹園<br />\nday2 竹園<br />\nday3 大崎下島<br />\nday4 宮島 &gt; HIJ &gt; HKG<br />\n<br />\n結果去到先發覺原來好多都可以好快行完<br />\n變成：<br />\nday1 HKG  &gt; HIJ &gt; 竹園<br />\nday2 竹園 &gt; 大久野島<br />\nday3 大崎下島 &gt; 宮島<br />\nday4 岩國 &gt; HIJ &gt; HKG<br />\n<br />\n兔島其實好快就撚完d兔，半日都唔洗<br />\n宮島睇完個日落就算，我幾年前去上埋山都係玩得半日"},{"pid":"57a6e5b9ff2af0faf03998c8969b1d60bf7c13b1","tid":124884,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/74ghy1zf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F74ghy1zf&h=b45a3809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩食完野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fe4b1040e69211bb361a7c719cc64d4b61a417","tid":124884,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"我下個月去兩日<br />\nplan完自己都覺得痴線<br />\n<br />\nday1 岡山-&gt;大久野島-&gt;宮島<br />\nday2 岩國城-&gt;縮景園，廣島城，原爆屋頂-&gt;大和博物館<br />\n<br />\n好似日日要七點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲想去埋三瀧寺<br />\n不過無咩可能去到"},{"pid":"c26e6eb0c25d3b4fedea67d77c73e809b4cbe34f","tid":124884,"uid":23473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"我五日<br />\n三夜，一日宮島一日吳市一日廣島原爆加市中心，廣島城，仲有咩去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2e6a1ef461104e636b13f131c4733242b329f7","tid":124884,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我五日<br />\n三夜，一日宮島一日吳市一日廣島原爆加市中心，廣島城，仲有咩去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街我8日可以去邊"},{"pid":"4a55bbc8d552be05db27b3bc3b22591b97ed77fd","tid":124884,"uid":49754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:46:07.000Z","msg":"廣島有張 3日tourist pass wide 3000 yen<br />\n包廣電/宮島船同巴士, 長途巴士(兔仔島都去到, 雖然一日得3班車對開, 但夾好時間就ok, 樓主住本通近長途巴士站用呢隻pass應該幾方便, 可以考慮下)"},{"pid":"f806418b4e4b06ade0f85054f4c819ec8996a603","tid":124884,"uid":31376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/jry86dn5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjry86dn5&h=0728b832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去宮島一定要食呢間牡丹屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都係其他巴打推介比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個set好似有11隻蠔，分幾種煮法</blockquote><br />\n我覺得麻麻"},{"pid":"cf4ec06133133be7d6c75002b05751caa6af5646","tid":124884,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"去行吓尾道都唔錯 反正廣島市冇嘢玩"},{"pid":"52371ac16b4651362fee0021e210957e2b0bb3b8","tid":124884,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"兔島你諗係幾點去到幾點?"},{"pid":"85835cc91850217eeda097ad6f9a4a30967bc22b","tid":124884,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣島有張 3日tourist pass wide 3000 yen<br />\n包廣電/宮島船同巴士, 長途巴士(兔仔島都去到, 雖然一日得3班車對開, 但夾好時間就ok, 樓主住本通近長途巴士站用呢隻pass應該幾方便, 可以考慮下)</blockquote><br />\n仆街，我買左1000yen果個<br />\n我女朋友屌到我仆街<br />\n要再買個3000yen既<br />\n即係浪漫了每人1000yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f6be4471c913261dc84f62500ae470c3f4b3a6","tid":124884,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兔島你諗係幾點去到幾點?</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩趕尾班車走<br />\n而家就到廣島市中心<br />\n兔島我今日玩足一日呀<br />\n頭班車去，尾班車返<br />\n玩一日都ok"},{"pid":"492f508a4a815cafbc7a13d9aba485348c88c626","tid":124884,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bc1p0sme\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbc1p0sme&h=1b1bb98d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9ac8e0685cf4e88ad64ab9560f0238e90b31d92","tid":124884,"uid":11299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兔島你諗係幾點去到幾點?</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩趕尾班車走<br />\n而家就到廣島市中心<br />\n兔島我今日玩足一日呀<br />\n頭班車去，尾班車返<br />\n玩一日都ok</blockquote><br />\n車程來回連船， 差唔多要5~6 粒鐘😂😂"},{"pid":"68c72457ae8fe10766479bae3ce9c224a6e363b4","tid":124884,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dFRH0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dFRH0V.jpg&h=07790020&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ebfbba7b647edfe0f816606445c38b6c71fc2f9","tid":124884,"uid":11299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我下個月去兩日<br />\nplan完自己都覺得痴線<br />\n<br />\nday1 岡山-&gt;大久野島-&gt;宮島<br />\nday2 岩國城-&gt;縮景園，廣島城，原爆屋頂-&gt;大和博物館<br />\n<br />\n好似日日要七點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲想去埋三瀧寺<br />\n不過無咩可能去到</blockquote><br />\n大久野 同 宮島<br />\n一東一西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩國， 宮島就Ok<br />\n不過岩岩錦帶橋纜車維修冇開"},{"pid":"544d74e0e8449198afe4cd9abff0b7a9a0baeff6","tid":124884,"uid":11299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dFRH0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dFRH0V.jpg&h=07790020&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我住後邊間酒店<br />\n但我冇黎食廣島燒"},{"pid":"9fce920969329d51efa2231a7a7f7eb822b8a12d","tid":124884,"uid":53333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我下個月去兩日<br />\nplan完自己都覺得痴線<br />\n<br />\nday1 岡山-&gt;大久野島-&gt;宮島<br />\nday2 岩國城-&gt;縮景園，廣島城，原爆屋頂-&gt;大和博物館<br />\n<br />\n好似日日要七點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲想去埋三瀧寺<br />\n不過無咩可能去到</blockquote><br />\n大久野 同 宮島<br />\n一東一西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩國， 宮島就Ok<br />\n不過岩岩錦帶橋纜車維修冇開</blockquote><br />\n維修到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後日就出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預23號去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3856eb8dbacc08bb98331ce82cf30f199a130c","tid":124884,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我下個月去兩日<br />\nplan完自己都覺得痴線<br />\n<br />\nday1 岡山-&gt;大久野島-&gt;宮島<br />\nday2 岩國城-&gt;縮景園，廣島城，原爆屋頂-&gt;大和博物館<br />\n<br />\n好似日日要七點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲想去埋三瀧寺<br />\n不過無咩可能去到</blockquote><br />\n大久野 同 宮島<br />\n一東一西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩國， 宮島就Ok<br />\n不過岩岩錦帶橋纜車維修冇開</blockquote><br />\n維修到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後日就出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預23號去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下個月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申月頭去中伏"},{"pid":"76e04c493263677cf737d0cbcf579e2bdb9b9a2a","tid":124884,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我下個月去兩日<br />\nplan完自己都覺得痴線<br />\n<br />\nday1 岡山-&gt;大久野島-&gt;宮島<br />\nday2 岩國城-&gt;縮景園，廣島城，原爆屋頂-&gt;大和博物館<br />\n<br />\n好似日日要七點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲想去埋三瀧寺<br />\n不過無咩可能去到</blockquote><br />\n大久野 同 宮島<br />\n一東一西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩國， 宮島就Ok<br />\n不過岩岩錦帶橋纜車維修冇開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為中間要去廣島間酒店放低行李<br />\n所以去宮島會近過岩國掛<br />\n<br />\nbetween<br />\n我去大久野島應該去得個半鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己一個對D兔仔興趣唔大<br />\n係想去個發電廠影下相<br />\n其實有無人睇住唔比入?"},{"pid":"db4443feb4cd3b44c0a047c855804e396124c087","tid":124884,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我下個月去兩日<br />\nplan完自己都覺得痴線<br />\n<br />\nday1 岡山-&gt;大久野島-&gt;宮島<br />\nday2 岩國城-&gt;縮景園，廣島城，原爆屋頂-&gt;大和博物館<br />\n<br />\n好似日日要七點起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲想去埋三瀧寺<br />\n不過無咩可能去到</blockquote><br />\n大久野 同 宮島<br />\n一東一西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩國， 宮島就Ok<br />\n不過岩岩錦帶橋纜車維修冇開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為中間要去廣島間酒店放低行李<br />\n所以去宮島會近過岩國掛<br />\n<br />\nbetween<br />\n我去大久野島應該去得個半鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己一個對D兔仔興趣唔大<br />\n係想去個發電廠影下相<br />\n其實有無人睇住唔比入?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人睇冇閉路有欄圍住守唔守規矩就自已諗<br />\n間唔中有個職員會踩單車環島餵兔<br />\n其餘時間都少人經過"},{"pid":"c6dc51d31a80774338d835a06bfaf64f34926c47","tid":124884,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兔島你諗係幾點去到幾點?</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩趕尾班車走<br />\n而家就到廣島市中心<br />\n兔島我今日玩足一日呀<br />\n頭班車去，尾班車返<br />\n玩一日都ok</blockquote><br />\n以為你未出發<br />\n見你話想下午去其他地方但又唔搭新幹線想提你諗清楚行程<br />\n廣島出發搭JR 2個鐘先到忠海<br />\n仲要夾班次同埋船真係可以用足一日時間"}]}